{"tid":53071,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"連續食左5日雞肉","createTime":"2016-12-24T12:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T17:02:20.000Z","uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"669310281475fb0f8098f72400b339273a7f6f1e","tid":53071,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:38:40.000Z","msg":"無食其他野，輕左8磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨係覺得蒸熟雞柳好食<br />\n<br />\n咁樣食返其他野係咪會反彈得好快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8df46b6151f246ce396280e192643148d629f1b6","tid":53071,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"呢排啲雞有耐藥菌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507f703bfbf749e982a9f3dd107a89148ac6e4d9","tid":53071,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢排啲雞有耐藥菌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我買果啲係惠康買果啲超平雞柳，食左幾日無事應該會事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc65cabbf86fc9b405aff226c0b1ccbe71ff144","tid":53071,"uid":20640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T12:48:40.000Z","msg":"白烚好似食擦膠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adc9d84bfbca093b6553675ba82538c522365ca","tid":53071,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>白烚好似食擦膠咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，我認難呑左少少，但係好鐘意佢隻味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8dbb19225d9fd3225269103ec964c07d4b1790b","tid":53071,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T13:38:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>呢排啲雞有耐藥菌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我買果啲係惠康買果啲超平雞柳，食左幾日無事應該會事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人類總是<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"198e73bbdf31163598a07bbcf9b3431e96567acf","tid":53071,"uid":32780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>呢排啲雞有耐藥菌喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我買果啲係惠康買果啲超平雞柳，食左幾日無事應該會事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人類總是<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未死得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}